<p><ent>Arraign</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Arraign
<hw>Ar*raign"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[From OF.
<ets>aramier</ets>, fr. LL. <ets>adhramire</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Old Eng.
Law)</fld> <def>To appeal to; to demand; <as>as, to <ex>arraign</ex> an
assize of novel disseizin</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Arraigner</ent>⟦br⟧
